17
00:01:12,578 --> 00:01:16,199
SO THE FIRST BIG IDEA IS:
ASK YOURSELF,

18
00:01:16,200 --> 00:01:18,960
WHAT'S THE WORST THING THAT CAN HAPPEN?

19
00:01:18,959 --> 00:01:23,559
I REMEMBER THE FIRST YEAR IN COLLEGE
CONSTANTLY WORRYING ABOUT MY GRADES.

20
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:27,469
WHAT WAS I GOING TO DO IF I GOT A B+
INSTEAD OF AN A?

21
00:01:27,469 --> 00:01:34,469
