AND I WOULD NEVER AMOUNT TO ANYTHING IN LIFE.

22
00:01:34,540 --> 00:01:39,900
LIKE, THAT WAS SERIOUSLY THE THOUGHT PROCESS
GOING THROUGH MY 17 YEAR OLD HEAD.

23
00:01:39,900 --> 00:01:43,490
NOW FAST FORWARD FIVE YEARS,
I WAS CLEANING A FEW DAYS AGO

24
00:01:43,489 --> 00:01:47,000
AND FOUND MY DIPLOMA IN SOME WEIRD PLACE IN
MY HOUSE.

25
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:50,478
HAVEN'T EVEN OPENED THE BOX SINCE I GOT IT,
AND WILL NEVER EVEN END UP USING IT FOR THE

26
00:01:50,478 --> 00:01:51,969
REST OF MY LIFE.

27
00:01:51,969 --> 00:01:54,719
THAT IS A PERFECT EXAMPLE OF WHAT YOUR BRAIN
DOES TO YOU.

28
00:01:54,719 --> 00:02:00,039
IT STARTS TO FREAK OUT WITH UNCERTAINTY.
IF YOU DON'T CLEARLY DEFINE THE WORST THING,

29
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:03,780
YOUR BRAIN WILL FIND A WAY TO EQUATE YOU GETTING
A B+

30
00:02:03,780 --> 00:02:06,859
TO YOU COMPLETELY RUINING YOUR LIFE.

31
00:02:06,859 --> 00:02:11,250
BUT IN REALITY, THE WORST THING IS NEVER REALLY
THAT BAD.

32
00:02:11,250 --> 00:02:15,250
I GET MESSAGES ALL THE TIME FROM PEOPLE SAYING,
"HEY, I'M REALLY INSPIRED BY YOUR CHANNEL."

33
00:02:15,250 --> 00:02:19,528
"I WANT TO START MY OWN, BUT I'M EXPERIENCING
A LOT OF RESISTANCE."

34
00:02:19,528 --> 00:02:25,049
AND HERE'S THE THING... SO DID I.
YOUR BRAIN'S DEFAULT IS LITERALLY TO THINK,

35
00:02:25,049 --> 00:02:29,718
"I WILL MAKE A VIDEO. PEOPLE WILL HATE IT."
"EVERYONE WILL MAKE FUN OF ME."

36
00:02:29,718 --> 00:02:33,658
"PEOPLE WILL GET ANGRY."
"THEY WILL COME AND BURN DOWN MY HOUSE."

37
00:02:33,658 --> 00:02:38,628
LIKE SERIOUSLY, THOSE ARE YOUR EITHER CONSCIOUS
OR SUBCONSCIOUS THOUGHTS.

38
00:02:38,628 --> 00:02:42,328
WHAT IS THE REALITY THOUGH?
THE WORST THING THAT WILL HAPPEN TO YOU

39
00:02:42,329 --> 00:02:46,730
IN REALITY IS A NEGATIVE COMMENT.
THAT IS IT.

40
00:02:46,729 --> 00:02:50,479
AND IT'S THE SAME THING WITH EVERYTHING ELSE
LIKE STARTING A BUSINESS,

41
00:02:50,479 --> 00:02:53,938
OR GIVING A PUBLIC SPEECH.
I HAVE BASICALLY NO EXPERIENCE SPEAKING IN

42
