SUCK.
I MIGHT HAVE STAGE-FRIGHT, I MIGHT BE AWKWARD,

44
00:03:01,449 --> 00:03:04,638
BUT I WOULD NEVER, NEVER REFUSE TO DO IT.
WHY?

45
00:03:04,639 --> 00:03:09,049
BECAUSE WHAT'S THE WORST THING THAT CAN HAPPEN?
IT'S NOT THAT THE WHOLE WORLD IS GOING TO

46
00:03:09,049 --> 00:03:12,260
MAKE FUN OF ME,
IT'S NOT THAT PEOPLE ARE GOING TO TRY TO KILL

47
00:03:12,259 --> 00:03:15,248
ME
EVERYWHERE I GO AFTER MY SPEECH. NO!

48
00:03:15,248 --> 00:03:19,168
IT'S SOME GUY IN THE CROWD WHO NEVER EVEN
GOT INVITED UP ON THE STAGE

49
00:03:19,169 --> 00:03:24,120
THINKING THAT MY SPEECH ISN'T THAT GREAT!!
LIKE WHO CARES?!

50
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:28,308
SO LET ME GIVE YOU ANOTHER EXAMPLE...
OUR WASHING MACHINE BROKE DOWN.

51
