55
00:03:43,528 --> 00:03:46,568
NOW YOU'LL NEVER HAVE CLEAN CLOTHES AGAIN.

56
00:03:46,568 --> 00:03:50,908
LOOK,
I SPENT THE FIRST 17 YEARS OF MY LIFE

57
00:03:50,908 --> 00:03:55,620
WASHING MY CLOTHES WITH MY HANDS
WITH SOME SHITTY RUSSIAN DETERGENT.

58
00:03:55,620 --> 00:04:00,079
SO WHAT'S THE WORST THING THAT CAN HAPPEN?
THAT I HAVE TO WASH A COUPLE OF SHIRTS

59
