OTHER AWESOME SHIRTS IN MY CLOSET?

62
00:04:12,139 --> 00:04:16,290
I MEAN, IT'S SO RIDICULOUS!
ALWAYS ASK YOURSELF,

63
00:04:16,290 --> 00:04:20,220
WHAT'S THE WORST THING THAT CAN HAPPEN?
CLEARLY DEFINE THE WORST OUTCOME,

64
00:04:20,220 --> 00:04:25,040
