"OKAY. LOOK. JUST STOP."

71
00:04:42,689 --> 00:04:46,839
CARNEGIE TELLS A STORY OF THIS GUY IN WWII,
WHO'S STUCK IN A SUBMARINE

72
00:04:46,839 --> 00:04:49,479
