78
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:12,199
EVERY SINGLE DAY!

79
00:05:12,199 --> 00:05:16,759
THE ONLY REASON IT'S NOT YOU
IS BECAUSE YOU WERE BORN IN A CERTAIN PLACE

80
00:05:16,759 --> 00:05:19,509
AND THEY WEREN'T.
THAT'S IT!

81
00:05:19,509 --> 00:05:21,269
NOW GOING BACK TO MY FRIEND,
I TOLD HIM,

82
00:05:21,269 --> 00:05:25,560
"LOOK, HERE'S WHAT I WANT YOU TO DO."
"EVERY DAY, YOU WILL START YOUR MORNING

83
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:29,100
BY WATCHING SOMEBODY'S HEAD BEING CHOPPED
OFF."

84
00:05:29,100 --> 00:05:32,480
