IF YOU START YOUR DAY BY

94
00:06:00,019 --> 00:06:03,629
WATCHING SOMEONE ELSE
HAVE THEIR HEAD CHOPPED OFF,

95
00:06:03,629 --> 00:06:10,159
NOTHING AND I MEAN ABSOLUTELY NOTHING
COULD POSSIBLY HAPPEN TO YOU FOR THE REST

96
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:12,750
OF THE DAY
